728055f-a.title: Queens: Sutphin Boulevard - Jamaica Avenue
728055f-a.text:
Sutphin Boulevard, south from Jamaica Avenue, showing this
Jamaica business thoroughfare. The tall building on the right is
the Long IIsland Railroad station, at the S.W. corner of Archer
A7enue and the elevated is that of the Long Island Railroad. Note
the row of taxicabs parked between 9lst ahd Archer Avenues.
MAY BE REPRODUCED  About 1927
